<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Zohar_texts">Zohar texts</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Zohar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: Zohar texts"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
